    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to be listing this absolute gem. It\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014truly spotless inside and out. It\u2019s been pampered and drives like a total dream! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see just how beautiful it is in person. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
