    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an immaculate E46 M3, a definitive driver\u2019s machine featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential with a 3.62 final drive ratio. Provenance is documented, highlighting a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension remains factory-spec with zero bushing deflection, providing the telepathic steering feedback these chassis are known for. Every seal, gasket, and mechanical tolerance is within factory parameters, presenting a turn-key opportunity for the serious collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
