    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in breathtaking condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the factory-original wheels are completely unblemished. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of 'like-new' luxury; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no signs of creasing or wear, and the interior still carries a fresh, clean aroma. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, function with Swiss-watch precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively at authorized intervals. With a documented history and all original keys and manuals included, this is a rare opportunity to own a pristine, investment-grade vehicle that satisfies even the most demanding inspection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
