    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken super good care of it, and it still has that fresh feel inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
