    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, maintained to a standard of mechanical perfection. This example features the S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system that operates with factory-spec timing precision. The drivetrain is headlined by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-Variable differential, providing exceptional power delivery. Proactive maintenance includes a reinforced rear subframe and rod bearing replacement, addressing the critical weak points of the chassis. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings and dampers, ensuring the razor-sharp handling characteristics this platform is known for. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a flawless factory finish, this is a turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
